COMMENTS ON TABLE <TABLE_NAME> IS <TEXT>;
COMMENTS ON COLUMN <TABLE_NAME.COLUMN_NAME> IS <TEXT>;


MAX-LENGTH: 4000



When the comment is already present on the object and we try to add, it will be overwritten.

Comments are stored in data dictionary.
to view them.


SELECT * FROM USER_TAB_COMMENTS;
SELECT * FROM USER_COL_COMMENTS;